title: THE WAY OF THE WARRIOR
itunes:title: THE WAY OF THE WARRIOR
itunes:subtitle: Motiversity
description:
"Rise champion. The way of the warrior. Champion eyes. Get back up. My spirit cries. Fear dies. Choked out by the scream. The desire to climb. And live out my dream. Take it for the team. Discipline reins. I want it too bad to listen to the pain. I'm a Warrior." – Billy Alsbrooks (https://bit.ly/BillyAlsbrooksMotiversity)


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic).
